data.description: Incredible 4 bedroom 2 bath Custom home on oversized corner lot and side entry garage. Split floor plan, Living and Dining room off entry and gourmet kitchen open to family room. Stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and Family room has a beautiful wood burning fireplace, volume ceilings and French doors that lead out to a covered screened patio area. Large owner suite with luxury bath complete with soaking tub and oversized shower, plus huge walk-in closet. Three nice size additional bedrooms, one is perfect for home office or den. The spacious backyard is completely fenced and has a storage shed for garden tools and lawn equipment. Great location and easy access to shopping and schools.
